  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Above The Horizon</strong> is survival, crafting and base building game where you must terraform the planet below you! <br> <br>Your terraforming team has landed safely, but you are stranded above the planet Lunaris with few essential resources to survive and help terraform the planet from above.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planet terraformation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft and build to terraform more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While you terraform you will be able to craft new things to <strong>survive, travel or terraform</strong> </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Above The Horizon</strong> is survival, crafting and base building game where you must terraform the planet below you! <br> <br>Your terraforming team has landed safely, but you are stranded above the planet Lunaris with few essential resources to survive and help terraform the planet from above.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planet terraformation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft and build to terraform more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While you terraform you will be able to craft new things to <strong>survive, travel or terraform</strong> </p></li></ul>",
